snippet.title: Welcome from Google Developers - Pittsburgh ML Summit ‘19
snippet.description:
Kyle Paul, Regional Lead of North America at Google, opens the ML ‘19 Summit in Pittsburgh, PA with a warm welcome and talks about the Developer Ecosystems team and programs that are at Google. Join us for some great talks, event goals, and more!
